product_name: Keen Waimea H2 Flip-Flops - Women's - 2013 Closeout
long_description: The Keen Waimea H2 Flip-Flops bring the comfort and toe protection of your favorite Keen water shoes to the sandy beach. Polyester webbing uppers perform well in wet conditions. Hydrophobic mesh linings are soft against bare feet. EVA footbeds are shaped to provide ample cushioning and arch support. Compression-molded EVA midsoles offer rich shock absorption and padding for all-day wear. Patented rubber toe guards protect feet from scuffs, bumps and uneven terrain. Nonmarking carbon rubber outsoles offer durability and superb traction. Closeout.
